    "e-festivals": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Festival Selection\n\n**IDFA 2025** — World Premiere\n\n**Hot Docs 2026** — International Competition\n\n**Sheffield Doc/Fest 2026** — Official Selection\n\n**DocLisboa 2026** — Iberian Premiere\n\n**True/False 2026** — Special Presentation\n\nDistributed by — Taskovski Films",
